{"tid":139920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【侵侵發功】強硬政策有阻嚇？ 一月非法入境人數跌27%","createTime":"2017-03-01T20:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T08:52:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c53ac2957424b3e72bf671433ec4b68c0c058b5","tid":139920,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T20:19:25.000Z","msg":"2017-03-01 15:49:17 HKT  <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170301/large/1488348548_2fc4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170301%2Flarge%2F1488348548_2fc4.jpg&h=da045e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n墨西哥與美國邊境。(美聯社)<br />\n美國海關及邊境保衞局（U.S. Customs and Border Protection）發表最新的非法移民人數統計，1月拘捕的非法入境人數，相對於12月減少了27%。<br />\n<br />\n數據顯示，當局於1月份拘捕想爬過邊境的非法移民人數為31,575人，較上個月減少了27%，而在入境關口但未能通過的移民亦減少了28%，至10,899人。<br />\n<br />\n不過，與2012至2016這幾年的1月份相比，今年的拘捕人數仍是最多。以往的統計指出，非法入境人數於寒冬時都會降低，並在春季重新攀升。<br />\n<br />\n同日另一份美國移民及海關執法局（U.S. ICE）監督報告指出，前總統奧巴馬任內，從2013年至2015年期間，有達160萬外國遊客逾期居留。據統計顯示，每年有超過40%的人本是合法入境，但因逾期逗留而變成非法。<br />\n<br />\n美國《華盛頓時報》"},{"pid":"b9bfd93348e1646057963b09906e2a7c9e6797dc","tid":139920,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T21:05:24.000Z","msg":"其實我睇過一份report，講有啲墨西哥非法入境者係會經常為工作etc進出美國，佢加強個左管制其實可能令到呢類非法入境者只好長期停留美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以起咩牆其實得反效果，更有效可能係deport佢地，不過其實只係比較有效，最終都係無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f027267e0958f6a3990c5d2b48ecf6defdb34363","tid":139920,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T03:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835e1a4fd37fdf4eb19b2f9d2190255949572e16","tid":139920,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T05:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8677ee9d188adc4b3a4171b247e41d4b2cfbbe","tid":139920,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:52:00.000Z","msg":"正經野無人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}